  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/01bbe919e3f551b95d84e58d9b37b0bf.avif?t=1708646337\" width=600 height=190 /></span><br>Arcane Array Arena is a rogue-like unit placement auto-battle game where you summon items in a magic circle and shoot them against your opponent.<br>Create your own unique item builds, compose the most powerful deployment, and defeat your opponents!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/d45751ec50c335323f026f71f9600ebe.avif?t=1708646337\" width=620 height=190 /></span><br>The game is divided into two main phases: the purchase phase and the competition phase. You purchase items at the store and place them in the magic circle. When you are ready, the battle begins!<br>The battle method is asynchronous, so you can fight at your own convenience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/b913bfa16c3b7d0b5a90688477ce9e78.avif?t=1708646337\" width=259 height=86 /></span><br>A variety of items exist and can be divided into several categories! <br>Synergy between items and their placement is the key to success!<strong></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/440804dad76443b57ddd85c0fb00e1be.poster.avif?t=1708646337\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/440804dad76443b57ddd85c0fb00e1be.webm?t=1708646337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/440804dad76443b57ddd85c0fb00e1be.mp4?t=1708646337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/01bbe919e3f551b95d84e58d9b37b0bf.avif?t=1708646337\" width=600 height=190 /></span><br>Arcane Array Arena is a rogue-like unit placement auto-battle game where you summon items in a magic circle and shoot them against your opponent.<br>Create your own unique item builds, compose the most powerful deployment, and defeat your opponents!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/d45751ec50c335323f026f71f9600ebe.avif?t=1708646337\" width=620 height=190 /></span><br>The game is divided into two main phases: the purchase phase and the competition phase. You purchase items at the store and place them in the magic circle. When you are ready, the battle begins!<br>The battle method is asynchronous, so you can fight at your own convenience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/b913bfa16c3b7d0b5a90688477ce9e78.avif?t=1708646337\" width=259 height=86 /></span><br>A variety of items exist and can be divided into several categories! <br>Synergy between items and their placement is the key to success!<strong></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/440804dad76443b57ddd85c0fb00e1be.poster.avif?t=1708646337\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/440804dad76443b57ddd85c0fb00e1be.webm?t=1708646337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2806840/extras/440804dad76443b57ddd85c0fb00e1be.mp4?t=1708646337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
